|blank1_name = GNIS feature ID |blank1_info = 1267308 |website = City of Canistota, South Dakota |footnotes = }} Canistota is a city in the eastern part of the U.S. state of South Dakota. It is located in McCook County, and 631 people lived there at the 2020 census.
